long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Streamline your Form 14A visa applications with this Chrome extension. Eliminate the need for extensive coordination and simplify the process for both sponsors and visitors requiring entry visa in Simplified in 5 Steps

For the Visitor:
1. Complete the online form: Start by filling out the Form 14A application at 
https://sg-form-filler.fly.dev/form/new.
2. Share the link: After submitting the form, you'll receive a unique link. Send this link to your local sponsor.

For the Local Sponsor (in Singapore):
3. Install the Chrome extension: Download and install the Form 14A Chrome extension from the Chrome Web Store.
4.Login & paste link: Log into your MyICA account. Then, open the Chrome extension and paste the unique link you received from the visitor.
5. Complete, pay & submit: Fill out the remaining details in the form, including uploading the visitor's photo and your local contact information. Make the required payment to submit the application.

That's it! Your visitor's entry visa application is now submitted and will be processed by the authorities
